OL,3,GLondon & South East
OL,4,
OL,5,CThis Evening and Tonight:FDry with
OL,6,Foften large amounts of cloud, but also
OL,7,Fclear spells will occur, which may
OL,8,Fallow patchy mist or fog to form in
OL,9,Frural areas later tonight. Winds will
OL,10,Fbe light.
OL,11,
OL,12,CFriday:FVarying, often large, amounts
OL,13,Fof thin cloud but still bright or
OL,14,Fsunny spells will occur. Slightly
OL,15,Fcooler along the coast with onshore
OL,16,Fwinds, becoming very warm or locally
OL,17,Fhot inland.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
OL,24,ANext Page  BWeather  CReg News  FReg TV
