OL,3,GLondon & South East
OL,4,
OL,5,COutlook for Saturday to Monday:FDry
OL,6,Fand bright Saturday, very warm or
OL,7,Flocally hot. On Sunday morning showery
OL,8,Frain clearing then risk of heavy
OL,9,Fshowers, feeling cooler. Monday
OL,10,Fprobably dry, sunny spells and very
OL,11,Fwarm.
